data.title: error
data.text:
This page does not exist

The requested link does not exist or the address had been changed. Maybe you had mistyped the request or you followed a link which is not anymore valid and supported...

In case the link was similar to "www.kinotv.com/../..cfm?namecode=...", please delete it. No .cfm - Links are valid, we had upgraded years ago our site from ColdFusion (cfm) to the more versatile MySQL and PHP (php) data bases. Unfortunately there was no reasonable way to re-direct the old cfm - Links to the new technique lautet, so we had to delete all this links.

If you are looking for a specific name or title, please enter the search in the designated searchbox in the upper left corner or follow the search option in the Menu. The Home - Option brings you to the entry page of KinoTV.

Thank you for your understanding.
